#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:323
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action   \n"
"**Range:** 120 feet   \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (an eggshell and a snakeskin glove)   \n"
"**Duration:** Concentration, up to 1 minute \n"
