"language you know. If the target is a plant, it gains the ability to move "
"its limbs, roots, vines, creepers, and so forth, and it gains senses similar "
"to a human's. Your GM chooses statistics appropriate for the awakened plant, "
"such as the statistics for the awakened shrub or the awakened tree.   \n"
