"target to a harmless demiplane. While there, the target is "
"incapacitated. The target remains there until the spell ends, at which point "
"the target reappears in the space it left or in the nearest unoccupied space "
"if that space is occupied.    \n"
"If the target is native to a different plane of existence than the one "
"you're on, the target is banished with a faint popping noise, returning to "
"its home plane. If the spell ends before 1 minute has passed, the target "
"reappears in the space it left or in the nearest unoccupied space if that "
