msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:3355 translations/spells.merged.md:4258
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 bonus action    \n"
"**Range:** 60 feet    \n"
"**Components:** V    \n"
"**Duration:** Instantaneous \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:3358
msgid ""
"A creature of your choice that you can see within range regains hit points "
"equal to 1d4 + your spellcasting ability modifier. This spell has no effect "
"on undead or constructs.  **At Higher Levels.** When you cast this spell "
