"30-foot cube within range. The pattern appears for a moment and "
"vanishes. Each creature in the area who sees the pattern must make a Wisdom "
"saving throw. On a failed save, the creature becomes charmed for the "
"duration. While charmed by this spell, the creature is incapacitated and has "
"a speed of 0.    \n"
"The spell ends for an affected creature if it takes any damage or if someone "
"else uses an action to shake the creature out of its stupor.\n"
msgstr ""

