msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:4024
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action    \n"
"**Range:** Touch    \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (a piece of cured leather)    \n"
"**Duration:** 8 hours \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:4026
msgid ""
"You touch a willing creature who isn't wearing armor, and a protective "
"magical force surrounds it until the spell ends. The target's base AC "
"becomes 13 + its Dexterity modifier. The spell ends if the target dons armor "
"or if you dismiss the spell as an action."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:4028
msgid "<!-- sources/spellcasting/spells/mage_hand.md -->"
msgstr ""

