#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:4511
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 bonus action    \n"
"**Range:** Self    \n"
"**Components:** V    \n"
"**Duration:** Instantaneous \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:4513
msgid ""
"Briefly surrounded by silvery mist, you teleport up to 30 feet to an "
"unoccupied space that you can see."
