msgid ""
"You make an area within range magically secure. The area is a cube that can "
"be as small as 5 feet to as large as 100 feet on each side. The spell lasts "
"for the duration or until you use an action to dismiss it.    \n"
"When you cast the spell, you decide what sort of security the spell "
"provides, choosing any or all of the following properties:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: translations/spells.merged.md:4980
msgid "Sound can't pass through the barrier at the edge of the warded area."
