#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action    \n"
"**Range:** Touch    \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (holy water or powdered silver and iron, which the "
"spell consumes)    \n"
"**Duration:** Concentration up to 10 minutes \n"
