#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5179
msgid "# Ray of Frost _Evocation cantrip_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5187
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"A frigid beam of blue-white light streaks toward a creature within "
"range. Make a ranged spell attack against the target. On a hit, it takes 1d8 "
"cold damage, and its speed is reduced by 10 feet until the start of your "
"next turn.    \n"
"The spell's damage increases by 1d8 when you reach 5th level (2d8), 11th "
"level (3d8), and 17th level (4d8). \n"
msgstr ""

