#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5204
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 minute    \n"
"**Range:** Touch    \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (a prayer wheel and holy water)    \n"
"**Duration:** 1 hour \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5207
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You touch a creature and stimulate its natural healing ability. The target "
"regains 4d8 + 15 hit points. For the duration of the spell, the target "
"regains 1 hit point at the start of each of its turns (10 hit points each "
"minute).    \n"
"The target's severed body members (fingers, legs, tails, and so on), if any, "
"are restored after 2 minutes. If you have the severed part and hold it to "
"the stump, the spell instantaneously causes the limb to knit to the "
"stump. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5209
msgid "<!-- sources/spellcasting/spells/reincarnate.md -->"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5214
msgid "name: Reincarnate level: 5 school: transmutation classes: druid"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5217
msgid "# Reincarnate _5th-level transmutation_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5222
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 hour    \n"
"**Range:** Touch    \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (rare oils and unguents worth at least 1,000 gp, "
"which the spell consumes)    \n"
"**Duration:** Instantaneous \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5225
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You touch a dead humanoid or a piece of a dead humanoid. Provided that the "
"creature has been dead no longer than 10 days, the spell forms a new adult "
"body for it and then calls the soul to enter that body. If the target's soul "
"isn't free or willing to do so, the spell fails.    \n"
"The magic fashions a new body for the creature to inhabit, which likely "
"causes the creature's race to change. The GM rolls a d100 and consults the "
"following table to determine what form the creature takes when restored to "
"life, or the GM chooses a form. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5242
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| d100   | Race                |\n"
"|--------|---------------------|\n"
"| 01-04  | Dragonborn          |\n"
"| 05-13  | Dwarf, hill         |\n"
"| 14-21  | Dwarf, mountain     |\n"
"| 22-25  | Elf, dark           |\n"
"| 26-34  | Elf, high           |\n"
"| 35-42  | Elf, wood           |\n"
"| 43-46  | Gnome, forest       |\n"
"| 47-52  | Gnome, rock         |\n"
"| 53-56  | Half-elf            |\n"
"| 57-60  | Half-orc            |\n"
"| 61-68  | Halfling, lightfoot |\n"
"| 69-76  | Halfling, stout     |\n"
"| 77-96  | Human               |\n"
"| 97-100 | Tiefling            |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5244
msgid ""
"The reincarnated creature recalls its former life and experiences. It "
"retains the capabilities it had in its original form, except it exchanges "
"its original race for the new one and changes its racial traits accordingly."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5246
msgid "<!-- sources/spellcasting/spells/remove_curse.md -->"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5254
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"name: Remove Curse\n"
"level: 3\n"
"school: abjuration\n"
"classes: cleric\n"
"         paladin\n"
"         warlock\n"
"         wizard\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5257
msgid "# Remove Curse _3rd-level abjuration_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5264
msgid ""
"At your touch, all curses affecting one creature or object end. If the "
"object is a cursed magic item, its curse remains, but the spell breaks its "
"owner's attunement to the object so it can be removed or discarded."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5266
