"name: Revivify\n"
"level: 3\n"
"school: necromancy\n"
"classes: cleric\n"
"         paladin\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5356
msgid "# Revivify _3rd-level necromancy_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5361
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action    \n"
"**Range:** Touch    \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (diamonds worth 300 gp, which the spell consumes)    "
"\n"
"**Duration:** Instantaneous \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5363
msgid ""
"You touch a creature that has died within the last minute. That creature "
"returns to life with 1 hit point. This spell can't return to life a creature "
"that has died of old age, nor can it restore any missing body parts."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:5365
msgid "<!-- sources/spellcasting/spells/rope_trick.md -->"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
