#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6248
msgid "# Teleportation Circle _5th-level conjuration_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6253
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 minute    \n"
"**Range:** 10 feet    \n"
"**Components:** V, M (rare chalks and inks infused with precious gems with "
"50 gp, which the spell consumes)    \n"
"**Duration:** 1 round \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6257
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"As you cast the spell, you draw a 10-foot-diameter circle on the ground "
"inscribed with sigils that link your location to a permanent teleportation "
"circle of your choice whose sigil sequence you know and that is on the same "
"plane of existence as you. A shimmering portal opens within the circle you "
"drew and remains open until the end of your next turn. Any creature that "
"enters the portal instantly appears within 5 feet of the destination circle "
"or in the nearest unoccupied space if that space is occupied.    \n"
"Many major temples, guilds, and other important places have permanent "
"teleportation circles inscribed somewhere within their confines. Each such "
"circle includes a unique sigil sequence--a string of magical runes arranged "
"in a particular pattern. When you first gain the ability to cast this spell, "
"you learn the sigil sequences for two destinations on the Material Plane, "
"determined by the GM. You can learn additional sigil sequences during your "
"adventures. You can commit a new sigil sequence to memory after studying it "
"for 1 minute.    \n"
"You can create a permanent teleportation circle by casting this spell in the "
"same location every day for one year. You need not use the circle to "
"teleport when you cast the spell in this way.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6259
msgid "<!-- sources/spellcasting/spells/thaumaturgy.md -->"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6264
msgid "name: Thaumaturgy level: 0 school: transmutation classes: cleric"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6267
msgid "# Thaumaturgy _Transmutation cantrip_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6272
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action    \n"
"**Range:** 30 feet    \n"
"**Components:** V    \n"
"**Duration:** Up to 1 minute \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6274
msgid ""
"You manifest a minor wonder, a sign of supernatural power, within range. You "
"create one of the following magical effects within range:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6281
msgid "Your voice booms up to three times as loud as normal for 1 minute."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6281
msgid "You cause flames to flicker, brighten, dim, or change color for 1 minute."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6281
msgid "You cause harmless tremors in the ground for 1 minute."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6281
msgid ""
"You create an instantaneous sound that originates from a point of your "
"choice within range, such as a rumble of thunder, the cry of a raven, or "
"ominous whispers."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6281
msgid ""
"You instantaneously cause an unlocked door or window to fly open or slam "
"shut."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6281
msgid "You alter the appearance of your eyes for 1 minute."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6283
msgid ""
"If you cast this spell multiple times, you can have up to three of its "
"1-minute effects active at a time, and you can dismiss such an effect as an "
"action."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6286
msgid "<!-- sources/spellcasting/spells/thunderwave.md -->"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6294
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"name: Thunderwave\n"
"level: 1\n"
"school: evocation\n"
"classes: bard\n"
"         druid\n"
"         sorcerer\n"
"         wizard\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6297
msgid "# Thunderwave _1st-level evocation_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6302
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action    \n"
"**Range:** Self (15-foot cube)    \n"
"**Components:** V, S    \n"
"**Duration:** Instantaneous \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6305
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"A wave of thunderous force sweeps out from you. Each creature in a 15-foot "
"cube originating from you must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed "
"save, a creature takes 2d8 thunder damage and is pushed 10 feet away from "
"you. On a successful save, the creature takes half as much damage and isn't "
"pushed.    \n"
"In addition, unsecured objects that are completely within the area of effect "
"are automatically pushed 10 feet away from you by the spell's effect, and "
"the spell emits a thunderous boom audible out to 300 feet. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6307
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**At Higher Levels.** When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd "
"level or higher, the damage increases by 1d8 for each slot level above "
"1st. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6309
msgid "<!-- sources/spellcasting/spells/time_stop.md -->"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6315
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"name: Time Stop\n"
"level: 9\n"
"school: transmutation\n"
"classes: sorcerer\n"
"         wizard\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6318
msgid "# Time Stop _9th-level transmutation_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6323 translations/spells.merged.md:6810
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action    \n"
"**Range:** Self    \n"
"**Components:** V    \n"
"**Duration:** Instantaneous \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: translations/spells.merged.md:6326
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You briefly stop the flow of time for everyone but yourself. No time passes "
"for other creatures, while you take 1d4 + 1 turns in a row, during which you "
"can use actions and move as normal.    \n"
"This spell ends if one of the actions you use during this period, or any "
"effects that you create during this period, affects a creature other than "
"you or an object being worn or carried by someone other than you. In "
"addition, the spell ends if you move to a place more than 1,000 feet from "
"the location where you cast it. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
